OL,3,CMan found guilty of 'despicable'
OL,4,Cmurder following house fire in Annan
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of the
OL,7,F'senseless' and 'dispicable' murder of
OL,8,Fa 58-year-old man whose body was found
OL,9,Finside a house that was ablaze.
OL,11,FThe actions of Gabriel Brown, 35, have
OL,12,Fbeen described by Police Scotland as
OL,13,F'senseless' and 'despicable'.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,16,Ffire at a property on Lady Street in
OL,17,FAnnan at around 6.55am on Tuesday
OL,18,FNovember 19 2024.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
