PN,32202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784110701
OL,3,CMan found guilty of 'despicable'
OL,4,Cmurder following house fire in Annan
OL,6,FJoseph Ernest Johnston was found
OL,7,Finside and he was pronounced dead at
OL,8,Fthe scene.
OL,10,FAn inquest into Mr Johnston's death
OL,11,Fthe following month found that he had
OL,12,Fdied from stab wounds to the neck.
OL,14,FIn addition to murder, Brown was also
OL,15,Ffound guilty of attempting to defeat
OL,16,Fthe ends of justice at the High Court
OL,17,Fin Glasgow today (Tuesday 14 July).
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
