PN,32203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784110701
OL,3,CMan found guilty of 'despicable'
OL,4,Cmurder following house fire in Annan
OL,6,FSpeaking after the verdict, Senior
OL,7,FInvestigating Officer, Detective
OL,8,FInspector Graeme Robertson from Police
OL,9,FScotland, said: "Brown's actions were
OL,10,Fcompletely senseless and reckless and
OL,11,Fled to the loss of Joseph's life. He
OL,12,Fwill now face the consequences of his
OL,13,Fdespicable actions.
OL,15,F"While this verdict does not change
OL,16,Fthe outcome, I hope it brings Joseph's
OL,17,Ffamily some form of comfort."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
